00:24:11.000 --> 00:24:15.000
people is Mohammad Darawshe. He’s a close friend and
role model for Meron. They’re united by their

00:24:16.000 --> 00:24:20.000
joint efforts for peace between Palestinians 
and Jews. The attacks on 7 October hit him very 

