00:28:10.000 --> 00:28:17.000
disagreement. Letting others have their say, even if
they disagree with you. Meron Mendel thinks this 

00:28:18.000 --> 00:28:32.000
principle is often neglected in Israel.

00:28:33.000 --> 00:28:37.000
This is demonstrated most clearly in the West Bank.
